'''extend_vehicle_life''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

Extends every vehicles live by x years. takes values between 0 and 100
~dihedral 18:40, 7 January 2008 (CET)

<pre>
[extend_vehicle_life]
extend_vehicle_life = 0
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [0 <= n <= 100]

'''Default:''' 0

